Spring MVC
        1. framework for buildng web applications in java
        2. based on model-view-contoller design pattern
        3. leverages(borrow) features of the core spring framework () 
        
Benefits:
    spring way of building web app UI's in java
    Leverages a set of reusable UI components
    Help manage application state for web req
    Process form data : validation,conversion
    Flexible configuration for the view layer
    
Components of Spring MVC
    1. a set of web pages
    2. collection of spring beans
    3. spring configuration